body:
I propose that Garen should still be able to buy it in the item shop. Upon purchasing DFG, your name becomes "DF Garen" in chat and you receive a passive "DFGaren" bonus that gives you 1 additional AP. If you scroll over it, the passive says, "You're a wizard, Garen."

I feel that this change is crucial in order to maintain game balance, not only for Garen, but for league as a whole. 
